    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278360/extras/36c58d56c0b0dfabd77a71c6a48bc936.avif?t=1756938557\" width=616 height=66 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to the Colony. You've been assigned by the Colony to record evidence of unknown aliens with your Colony issued camera. Every day you will be given a new quota that you will need to satisfy. You will be given a certain amount of cash based off of your recordings. You can use your hard earned cash to buy helpful items from the shop located in your ship's terminal. You can buy and use things like bear traps and stun guns to set up traps for the aliens while you stealthily record them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278360/extras/f15cd11be9ce5587e6b81429eb4b73c7.poster.avif?t=1756938557\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278360/extras/f15cd11be9ce5587e6b81429eb4b73c7.webm?t=1756938557\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278360/extras/f15cd11be9ce5587e6b81429eb4b73c7.mp4?t=1756938557\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278360/extras/ea0cf6076efdbb4740e5f974fafd40bd.poster.avif?t=1756938557\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278360/extras/ea0cf6076efdbb4740e5f974fafd40bd.webm?t=1756938557\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278360/extras/ea0cf6076efdbb4740e5f974fafd40bd.mp4?t=1756938557\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278360/extras/6aafa9712893766c081f102e302f541d.avif?t=1756938557\" width=616 height=66 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Taking on this difficult task alone is possible, but discouraged. Your fellow colonists can watch your back while you record. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278360/extras/3789ff27ceee2939f874e08118f2a315.avif?t=1756938557\" width=616 height=66 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep the footage even when your crew dies. Your lost footage will be recovered by the Colony. At the end of every day, you can watch your footage in real time with your crew.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278360/extras/ca3e56d88660c0048830dad67fec8da9.poster.avif?t=1756938557\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278360/extras/ca3e56d88660c0048830dad67fec8da9.webm?t=1756938557\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278360/extras/ca3e56d88660c0048830dad67fec8da9.mp4?t=1756938557\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
